Frequently Asked Questions about Yarra Ocean Suites Danang
Which popular attractions are close to Yarra Ocean Suites Danang?
Nearby attractions include Apocalypse Beach Club (0.05 miles), Marine Sky Bar (0.09 miles), and Danang Night Market (0.2 miles).
See all nearby attractions.
What are some of the property amenities at Yarra Ocean Suites Danang?
Some of the more popular amenities offered include a rooftop bar, free wifi, and a pool.
See all property amenities.
Which room amenities are available at Yarra Ocean Suites Danang?
Top room amenities include a minibar, air conditioning, and a flat screen TV.
See all room amenities.
What food & drink options are available at Yarra Ocean Suites Danang?
Guests can enjoy a rooftop bar, an on-site restaurant, and a lounge during their stay.
Learn more.
What are some restaurants close to Yarra Ocean Suites Danang?
Conveniently located restaurants include Ca Chuon Co Vietnamese - Seafood Restaurant., IVegan Super Shop, and The Windsor Tea House.
See all nearby restaurants.
Are there opportunities to exercise at Yarra Ocean Suites Danang?
Yes, guests have access to a pool, a fitness center, and a sauna during their stay.
Does Yarra Ocean Suites Danang have airport transportation?
Yes, Yarra Ocean Suites Danang offers airport transportation for guests. We recommend calling ahead to confirm details.
Is Yarra Ocean Suites Danang located near the city center?
Yes, it is 0.2 miles away from the center of My An.
Are any cleaning services offered at Yarra Ocean Suites Danang?
Yes, dry cleaning and laundry service are offered to guests.
Which languages are spoken by the staff at Yarra Ocean Suites Danang?
The staff speaks multiple languages, including English and Vietnamese.
Does Yarra Ocean Suites Danang have any great views?
Yes, guests often enjoy the harbor view available here.
